
To run the DataCapture program, you'll need to install the following dependencies:

Python 3.6 or higher
To install Python, follow the instructions on the official Python website: https://www.python.org/downloads/

To install pytest, open a terminal window and execute the following command:
```console
foo@bar:~$ pip install -r requirements.txt
foo
```
Running Tests
Once the dependencies are installed, you can run the tests using the following command:

```console
foo@bar:~$ pytest test_data_capture.py
foo
```